bits IgA responses and regulates the anti-fungal immune response.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Van Spriel, Annemiek B.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Sofi, Mariam", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Gartlan, Kate H.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Van Schaaf, Alie Der", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Verschueren, Ineke", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Torensma, Ruurd", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Raymakers, Reinier A P", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Loveland, Bruce E.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Netea, Mihai G.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Adema, Gosse J.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Wright, Mark D.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Figdor, Carl G.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Bat immunology", "Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/7b657cca71ef88f7c33f7672703057b0", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/244a417d39ea8f2d573260b96dd14f5b6170c78e06a0fba252a79fb5ab351741", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/4M4LX2UM", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/4M4LX2UM", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/9698bb8e41cc560f6388fa9c387a54e6!/b66402-68684", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "3", "pages": "1-11", "title": "PLoS Pathogens", "